<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Request Approved</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Your request has been approved</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ user.username }},</p>
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your request with the following details has been approved:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request ID: {{ request.id }}</li>
        <li>Start Date: {{ request.startDate|date('Y-m-d') }}</li>
        <li>End Date: {{ request.endDate|date('Y-m-d') }}</li>
        <!-- Add more details as needed -->
    </ul>
    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
</body>
</html>
